title: Drawing, "Female, Left Profile"
description: A dark line depicting both the profile contours and facial features is especially heavy in the eyebrow, extending sharply upward from the top of the nose to the hairline; the diagonal line from ear to chin level; and the neck and shoulders. A few thin, wavy lines indicate the hair on the back of the head, which is rounded.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Female, Left Profile".
15.3 x 14.4 cm (6 x 5 7/8 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-155.
